      <data key="d2">This page contains no text and serves as an empty placeholder. It is not informative and plays a passive role in the document, which discusses dropout techniques in neural networks in the surrounding pages.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-83c69fffa450fc3e8fcd39c90c9b5794</data>
