    <node id="Dropout Neural Network Error Rate Comparison on MNIST (image)">
      <data key="d0">Dropout Neural Network Error Rate Comparison on MNIST (image)</data>
      <data key="d1">image</data>
      <data key="d2">The graph visualizes the impact of using dropout on error rates for different neural network configurations on the MNIST test set, emphasizing improvements achieved through dropout techniques over traditional backpropagation.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-fb911a56b8223fdb7d604d0676aa9f13</data>
      <data key="d4">[2012]_ImageNet_Classification_with_Deep_Convolutional_Neural_Networks.pdf</data>
