      <data key="d0">Hinton MATLAB Code Reference (page_footnote)</data>
      <data key="d1">page_footnote</data>
      <data key="d2">This footnote provides a link to MATLAB code for a paper by Geoffrey Hinton, allowing readers to access practical resources for implementing dropout techniques discussed on page 8. It reinforces the methods described in the surrounding sections on neural network training.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-8001fb997a0ed1588298250eda7a8baf</data>
      <data key="d4">[2012]_ImageNet_Classification_with_Deep_Convolutional_Neural_Networks.pdf</data>
