      <data key="d1">page_footnote</data>
      <data key="d2">This footnote provides a link to the source code relevant to the Deep Belief Network discussed in the experiments, enhancing understanding and reproducibility of dropout techniques mentioned in the main text.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-02467b58f73bf477146d8153b6a4df54</data>
