      <data key="d0">TIMIT Speech Recognition Experiments (page_number)</data>
      <data key="d1">page_number</data>
      <data key="d2">This page outlines the use of the TIMIT dataset for speech recognition experiments, detailing data preprocessing and feature extraction strategies, which ties together the machine learning techniques introduced in the preceding sections.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-8e5722549700e5bc7e37e9b13238ac21</data>
      <data key="d4">[2012]_ImageNet_Classification_with_Deep_Convolutional_Neural_Networks.pdf</data>
