    <node id="Neural Network Feature Grid (image)">
      <data key="d0">Neural Network Feature Grid (image)</data>
      <data key="d1">image</data>
      <data key="d2">This image illustrates a grid of 100 random features extracted from a neural network after using a dropout technique. The grayscale patterns represent learned activations, confirming that dropout aids in learning more generalized and less co-adaptive features, aligning with the text's analysis on dropout's impact on feature learning.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-ad037fa9d0a9b9bd518b0761df880676</data>
      <data key="d4">[2012]_ImageNet_Classification_with_Deep_Convolutional_Neural_Networks.pdf</data>
