      <data key="d1">page_footnote</data>
      <data key="d2">This footnote cites the Kaldi toolkit, crucial for preprocessing the TIMIT dataset in speech recognition experiments. It underscores the significance of external resources in the methodology and provides a direct link for further exploration.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-4324355ff9a79ca59bfc951ab0af1a8d</data>
