      <data key="d1">page_number</data>
      <data key="d2">Page 10 continues the exploration of dropout finetuning techniques for pretrained neural networks, reflecting on performance improvements over backpropagation methods. It ties closely to discussions on the impact of dropout in enhancing model feature learning and generalization as established in preceding sections.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-bcd76e87b5dfbe4f0b91deef2b6ebd32</data>
