      <data key="d0">Finetuning Techniques and Experiments Overview (page_number)</data>
      <data key="d1">page_number</data>
      <data key="d2">Page 11 delves into the specifics of pretraining neural networks using RBMs and the effects of dropout finetuning, emphasizing their roles in reducing error rates and preventing overfitting. This page builds upon preceding discussions about neural network architecture and reinforces the overarching theme of optimizing machine learning for speech recognition.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-8c7ef621ed700ebe9bf301cd40f3e36a</data>
