    <node id="Momentum">
      <data key="d0">Momentum</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Momentum is an optimization strategy that helps accelerate gradients vectors in the right directions, thus leading to faster converging.&lt;SEP&gt;Momentum is related to the adjustment of learning rates in neural network training, influencing weight updates.&lt;SEP&gt;Momentum is a technique in optimization to accelerate gradient updates by considering past gradients, helping to navigate local minima and oscillations.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-7b67c60a2d1480f70415891941c5701d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dcbc540785e67a58a0e8941e3e7fcc4b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-334b34cebf9747d93cfba42c0f8c26c7</data>
